# VNElementType

**Enumeration**

An enumeration of the type of element in feature print data.

## Declaration

```swift
enum VNElementType
```

## Element Types

- **VNElementType.unknown**: The element type isn’t known.
- **VNElementType.float**: The elements are floating-point numbers.
- **VNElementType.double**: The elements are double-precision floating-point numbers.

## Creating an Element Type

- **init(rawValue:)**

## Determining Types of Feature Prints

- **elementType**: The type of each element in the data.
- **VNElementTypeSize(_:)**: Returns the size of a feature print element.

## Conforms To

- BitwiseCopyable
- Equatable
- Hashable
- RawRepresentable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
